"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-12-irelands-olympic-hero-daniel-wiffen-rushed-hospital-closing-ceremony-21405654\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Daniel Wiffen says he was 'incredibly disappointed' to miss out on the chance to be Ireland's flagbearer forthe closing ceremony of the Paris Olympicsafter being 'rushed to hospital' with an illness.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 84, \"end\": 91, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9968557894197534, \"rank\": 0.002856861554068458, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daniel Wiffen\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 13}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 67, \"to\": 77}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympicsafter\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 155}, {\"ngram\": \"hospital\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 181}, {\"ngram\": \"an illness\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old swimmer clinched gold in the men's 800m freestyle competition, setting a new Olympic record in the process, to add to the two World Championship titles he won in Doha earlier this year.\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.903888895673802e-16, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 23-year-old swimmer\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 224}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 238}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 800m freestyle competition\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 278}, {\"ngram\": \"a new Olympic record\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 308}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"the two World Championship titles\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also claimed the bronze medal in the men's 1,500m freestyle and became Ireland's first ever athlete to compete in the 10km open-water marathon, finishing in 18th place.\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9968557894197534, \"rank\": 0.002856861554068458, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 1,500m freestyle\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10km open-water marathon\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"18th place\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, after the gruelling swim in the River Seine,Wiffen described the experience as 'probably one of the worst things I have done'due to being repeatedly 'punched and kicked in the face'.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gruelling swim\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst things\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The race went ahead despite major concern surrounding the quality of the water in the river, withthe men's triathlon having to be postponed as a result of high levels of E.coli- which can cause pneumonia, sepsis or even meningitis.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The race\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"major concern\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"men's triathlon\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"high levels\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"pneumonia\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"sepsis\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"even meningitis\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several triathletes, including Vasco Vilaca, Hayden Wilde and Ainsley Thorpe, have since come down with illnesses and Wiffen was forced to miss last night's closing ceremony after being hospitalised with a 'bug'.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999774077992731, \"rank\": 2.223794216944181e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}, {\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Thorpe\", \"score\": 0.6249122632378461, \"rank\": 0.4637968576607522, \"text\": \"Thorpe\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Thorpe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Thorpe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several triathletes\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"Vasco Vilaca\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"illnesses\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"last night's closing ceremony\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'bug\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not known whether Wiffen's sickness is related to his participation in the open-water marathon.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wiffen's sickness\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"his participation\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"the open-water marathon\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks everyone who reached out, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m incredibly disappointed to miss out on the opportunity to be flag bearer last night.Yesterday I rushed to hospital as I was very unwell with a bug that I am being treated for, and am feeling better now.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"flag bearer\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"hospital\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"a bug\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope everyone enjoys the evening\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 'Thanks everyone who reached out, I am incredibly disappointed to miss out on the opportunity to be flagbearer last night,' Wiffen wrote on X, formerly known as Twitter.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.569320832177471e-13, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngram\": \"the evening\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 'Thanks\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"flagbearer\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Yesterday I rushed to hospital as I was very unwell with a bug that I am being treated for, and am feeling better now.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hospital\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"a bug\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I hope everyone enjoys the evening and I hope to be well enough to seeing everyone when we get home.'\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"the evening\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Double gold-medalist Fintan McCarthy replaced Wiffen as Ireland's flagbearer and led out his nation alongside bronze-winning swimmer Mona McSharry at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2018, \"end\": 2033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fintan McCarthy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\"}, {\"begin\": 2053, \"end\": 2060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9968557894197534, \"rank\": 0.002856861554068458, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2130, \"end\": 2143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mona McSharry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\"}, {\"begin\": 2151, \"end\": 2166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"his nation\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a separate post, Wiffen said he had realised a 'childhood dream' by representing Ireland at an Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2253, \"end\": 2260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9968557894197534, \"rank\": 0.002856861554068458, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a separate post\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2195}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'childhood dream\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'They say every child has a dream, to pursue the dream is in every child hand's to make it a reality.\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every child\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"the dream\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"every child hand\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had the dream of becoming an Olympic Champion.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dream\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2400}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Champion\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I put the work in every day and I am so happy to say that I have accomplished my childhood dream.\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2533, \"en